About page i guess


Name/nickname you could call me: Soul, souly

My favorite food: Cola, Chocolate
My favorite anime: K-on!, Katekyo hitman reborn, HxH, One piece, FMA
My favorite video game: Kingdom hearts, Darksouls
My music taste: Breakcore, Instrumental, Classic, Post-rock, Electronic
Sports I play include: Volley ball, Tennis, Basket ball
My on-going projects: Currently i'm planning on a beatmap project which is about some artist that is heavenly underrated
My other interests: language learning, psychology, biology, physics, art
My Discord is: Soul#2846

Likes in a person: Friendly, shares similar interests, likes to talk about anything, overall bright, likes rock
Dislikes in a person: Someone that swears alot, egoistic, elitists, pseudo-intellectuals, jokes around too much when there is a discussion

My personality: I sometimes like to talk alot, weather it's about osu! or any other various topics, i like to care for people i can be a bit nosy but that's because i care so much, i'm pretty defensive to people being douche's to my friends, i can misunderstand people sometimes, my phrasing is kinda off sometimes i like to play mania and play SM/O2jam/Lr2 aswell, i also map alot, i want to learn all game modes and currently learn how to map them all. i'm a 4k/7k main (obviously) but my favorite keymode is 5k.

Big thanks to these people who gifted me supporter! i love you guys ❤
Dionysaw for my first supporter and 2 months

chieftots for 3 months

Kouhaifox for a month

Gekido-Kun for a month

TheBestName for a month

Ranmi for a month

And the biggest thanks for Eternalie for gifting me 1 year of supporter! ❤
